overview: To think how hundreds of Southern freedom riders in the 1960's got clunked in the head with billy clubs on smelly public buses just so that their brothers, decades later, could enjoy round, thick, enticing white Valley Girl ass. That look on cover girl Kirra Lynne's face tells you only one thing. She's been to the mountain. History as well as a public spunk pool is about to be fashioned within her lush loins.
title: Inseminated By 2 Black Men 15
